      <title>监管机构称法国应终止 EDF 的电价管制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/france-should-end-edf-s-regulated-power-prices-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国竞争管理机构周二建议，法国政府应废除法国电力公司的管制电价，以增强来自其他供应商的竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/france-should-end-edf-s-regulated-power-prices-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 12:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
